OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FHeavy rain
OL,6,Fquickly clearing to the east this
OL,7,Fevening, then a mix of clear spells
OL,8,Fand showers, these continuing
OL,9,Fovernight. Showers heaviest and most
OL,10,Ffrequent in the northwest. Staying
OL,11,Fmild.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FA bright and breezy day,
OL,14,Fwith sunny spells and showers. Showers
OL,15,Fmost frequent in the north, some heavy
OL,16,Fwith the risk of hail and thunder.
OL,17,FFeeling warm in the sunshine.
